25:[["$","blockquote",null,{"children":["\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"阅读提示\n适合对象：在做 Linux 渗透、提权排查和本地利用学习的读者。\n阅读前提：会使用常见 Linux 命令并理解权限模型。\n核心收获：识别高频提权路径，并把自动化枚举与手工验证结合起来。\n说明：内核版本、发行版差异和补丁状态会直接影响利用结果。"}],"\n"]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"在渗透测试中，获取初始 Shell 往往只是一个低权限用户（如 www-data、nobody），要真正控制目标系统，我们需要进行权限提升（Privilege Escalation），将普通用户权限提升为 root。Linux 提权是一门系统化的技术，涉及文件权限、内核漏洞、系统配置缺陷等多个维度。本文将全面讲解 Linux 环境下的各种提权技术，从原理到实战，帮助你掌握从低权限到 root 的完整路径。"}],"\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"linux-权限模型基础","children":["Linux 权限模型基础",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#linux-权限模型基础","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"在开始提权之前，我们需要理解 Linux 的权限模型："}],"\n","$L2d","\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"提权信息收集","children":["提权信息收集",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#提权信息收集","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"在尝试提权之前，首先需要全面了解目标系统的配置。"}],"\n","$L2e","\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"suidsgid-提权","children":["SUID/SGID 提权",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#suidsgid-提权","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"SUID（Set User ID）是 Linux 提权中最经典的攻击面之一。当一个可执行文件设置了 SUID 位时，任何用户运行该程序时都会以文件所有者（通常是 root）的身份执行。"}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"查找-suid-文件","children":["查找 SUID 文件",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#查找-suid-文件","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L2f","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"gtfobins-利用","children":["GTFOBins 利用",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#gtfobins-利用","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":["GTFOBins（",["$","a",null,{"href":"https://gtfobins.github.io/%EF%BC%89%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%94%B6%E9%9B%86%E4%BA%86%E5%90%84%E7%A7%8D","children":"https://gtfobins.github.io/）是一个收集了各种"}]," Unix 二进制文件提权方法的项目。以下是常见的 SUID 提权示例："]}],"\n","$L30","\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"内核漏洞提权","children":["内核漏洞提权",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#内核漏洞提权","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"当系统内核版本较旧时，可能存在已知的内核漏洞可以直接获取 root 权限。"}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"检测内核版本","children":["检测内核版本",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#检测内核版本","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L31","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"dirtycowcve-2016-5195","children":["DirtyCow（CVE-2016-5195）",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#dirtycowcve-2016-5195","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"DirtyCow 是 Linux 内核中一个存在了近 10 年的竞态条件漏洞，影响 Linux 2.6.22 至 4.8.3 之间的所有内核版本。"}],"\n","$L32","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"dirtypipecve-2022-0847","children":["DirtyPipe（CVE-2022-0847）",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#dirtypipecve-2022-0847","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"DirtyPipe 影响 Linux 5.8 至 5.16.11 之间的内核版本，可以覆写任意只读文件。"}],"\n","$L33","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"使用自动化工具检测内核漏洞","children":["使用自动化工具检测内核漏洞",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#使用自动化工具检测内核漏洞","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L34","\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"cron-定时任务提权","children":["Cron 定时任务提权",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#cron-定时任务提权","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"Cron 定时任务是 Linux 系统的任务调度机制。如果 root 用户的 cron 任务执行的脚本对当前用户可写，就可以被利用来提权。"}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"发现可利用的-cron-任务","children":["发现可利用的 Cron 任务",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#发现可利用的-cron-任务","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L35","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"可写脚本提权","children":["可写脚本提权",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#可写脚本提权","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L36","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"path-劫持提权","children":["PATH 劫持提权",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#path-劫持提权","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"如果 cron 任务中的脚本调用了命令但没有使用绝对路径，可以通过修改 PATH 环境变量来劫持。"}],"\n","$L37","\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"环境变量提权","children":["环境变量提权",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#环境变量提权","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"path-劫持","children":["PATH 劫持","$L38"]}],"\n","$L39","\n","$L3a","\n","$L3b","\n","$L3c","\n","$L3d","\n","$L3e","\n","$L3f","\n","$L40","\n","$L41","\n","$L42","\n","$L43","\n","$L44","\n","$L45","\n","$L46","\n","$L47","\n","$L48","\n","$L49","\n","$L4a","\n","$L4b"]
